channel.title: How do i solve theese problems...(get:missing skills,the skillcapes,+other)
channel.description:
ok, first i need to know how to mod in skillcapes and the three missing skills.......
Then i need to know how to talk to the npcs so i can do the quests. (most of the npcs are missing,so i want them to come back)
then my last question, where do i find Client.Java ?
BTW... Some ladders are "broken", you cant climb them, also some stairs are f-ed up...
Magic does not work either.....
Thx for the help to thoose who answer my questions

item.title: How do i solve theese problems...(get:missing skills,the skillcapes,+other)
item.dc:creator: @jjones10 jjones10
item.description:
@jjones10 wrote:

Well… you base is pretty messed up but here it goes:
1)What does “mod in skillcapes” mean?
2)add your npc id and xy coords anywhere into your “autospawn.cfg” file in your server folder
3)In your folder with all the server files in it is where client.java is…

P.S. to make ladders work, you need to find out what case that action is in your client.java and add a tele command to that case
Hope i helped a little and sorry if i am wrong on anything
